      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this vehicle in showroom condition, representing the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and displaying no signs of wear, this specimen offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector. Every mechanical component and aesthetic detail has been preserved to an exacting standard, ensuring a level of refinement that is increasingly rare to encounter on the secondary market.",
