    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s an absolute stunner and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's honestly in pristine shape inside and out. If you're looking for something that feels basically brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 42900.0,
