    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a pristine example of automotive excellence, maintained to a standard rarely seen on the secondary market. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. There are no stone chips on the front fascia, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash, wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple without a single crease or bolster wear, and it still retains that signature factory-fresh aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the ambient lighting, operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is detailed to show-car standards, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. For the buyer who demands perfection, this is a turn-key investment that looks, feels, and performs exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
